# Golf Tournament Frontend

- Next.js App Router, TypeScript, Tailwind. See `FRONTEND_PROJECT_CONTEXT.md`.
- Backend: `NicolasEmmel/golf-tournament-backend` — inspect `docs/BACKEND_CONTRACT.md` before integration.
- Flutter repo is **visual/UX reference only**; do not copy its architecture.
- One shared SignalR connection via provider; no hub logic in leaf components.
- No frontend gross/net/handicap calculation; display backend values only.
- REST and SignalR calls live under `services/`; use typed models in `models/`.
- Prefer React Context + hooks over Redux unless requirements change.
- Do not commit `.env.local` or secrets. Use `NEXT_PUBLIC_*` only for public URLs.
- Implement one phase at a time; avoid speculative features.
